The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Sports | New role for Sachin
                                                                                                                                                                                                     New role for Sachin
                      
	New Delhi: Sachin Tendulkar has joined forces with the United Nations Childrens Fund (Unicef) to get children wash their hands for better health and hygiene as part of the first Global Handwashing Day on October 15.         
	Sachin is featured in a public service announcement, which will come up soon on television in 14 languages to garner support for the campaign targeting students in more than six million schools across the country.                                                                                                                          
